Census of human transcription factors

Census list of 1391 human DNA-binding transcription factors as described by Vaquerizas et al., 2009.

data(human.tf)

Format

A data frame with 6 columns and 1391 rows coorresponding to genes.

Source

Juan M. Vaquerizas, Sarah K. Kummerfeld, Sarah A. Teichmann & Nicholas M. Luscombe. A census of human transcription factors: function, expression and evolution. Nature Reviews Genetics 10, 252-263 (April 2009) | doi:10.1038/nrg2538

Examples

 data(human.tf)
